title: [A Glimpse of Glee, Mystic Whims]
description: Refined oak-paneled walls rise from a white limestone floor.  Just above a grey-veined white marble fountain hangs a tattered merchant permit, and a dark and light oak ceiling completes the picture.  A long carved oak counter and a gilded maple table stand side by side in the middle of the room.

Refined oak-paneled walls rise from a white limestone floor.  Just above a grey-veined white marble fountain hangs a curl-edged vellum wall map, and a dark and light oak ceiling completes the picture.  A long carved oak counter and a gilded maple table stand side by side in the middle of the room.
